posts.name: Jeff Zakrzewski
posts.cooked:
Use this: https://storage.googleapis.com/frc2025/NavX2025.json

It’s the same as the one at https://dev.studica.com/releases/2025/NavX.json , however they have a typo in the artifactId in the original - I literally changed a single “-” to a “_” and it works.

I assume they’ll fix this shortly as it just looks like a bad deployment - but the 1st link will work for now!
